reviewText: Very cool film, great intricate plot that keeps you interested!  Glad to have a copy of this not too well known film.  A must for George Nader fans!

Tip Not Included was released in 1966. It starred George Nader as Jerry Cotton the FBI agent on the track of crooks who hijacked a truck full of money. A fine B-Film. Fans of George Nader will like this the most.
